 Features:

 Daily Learning Streaks  Track your consistency and visualize progress on a weekly calendar.

 Topic-Based Learning  Focus on specific subjects or skills each week.

 Progress Tracking  Monitor what youve learned with colorful indicators and statistics.

 Modern SwiftUI Interface  Minimal, responsive design optimized for iPhone and iPad.
